    m_HorizontalOverflow: 0
    m_VerticalOverflow: 0
    m_LineSpacing: 1
  m_Text: "Game 1 \u2013 Trash Sorting\n\nClean the Beach!\n\nTrash is scattered
    everywhere and it's your job to clean it up.\nWalk over trash items to pick them
    up and carry them above your head.\n\nFind the correct trash bin and throw the
    trash inside.\n\n\u2714 Correct bin: +10 points\n\u2716 Wrong bin: \u221230 points\n\nBe
    careful! Your score cannot go below 0.\n\nThe player with the highest score when
    time runs out wins."
